From yvonnick.noel at uhb.fr  Mon May 23 11:09:35 2011
From: yvonnick.noel at uhb.fr (Yvonnick Noel)
Date: Mon, 23 May 2011 11:09:35 +0200
Subject: [R-gui] R2STATS: A New GUI for GLM and GLMM in R
Message-ID: <4DDA244F.2050107@uhb.fr>

Hello,

I don't know if it might be of interest to some of you, but I have begun 
to develop a very simple GUI for estimating GLM and GLMM in R, called 
R2STATS :

http://yvonnick.noel.free.fr/r2stats

It is based on gWidgets and RGtk2. I am sorry: It is only available in 
French at the moment but should be available in English in the next few 
months.

It is by no means as sophisticated or complete as other existing 
solutions, but is strongly oriented towards a model-comparison approach, 
with automatic graphs generation, which was what I needed for my students.

Best wishes,

Yvonnick Noel
Department of Psychology
University of Brittany, Rennes
France


